                            'He is the light in which there is no darkness, the living in whom there is no death, the good in whom there is no wickedness, the gentle in whom there is neither rebellion nor wrath, the meek in whom there is neither poison nor bitterness.',
                            'He sits in the far north, powerful, beautiful, and resplendent, the primordial container of all shining ones, the Father of All Uthras.',
